{"article_id":"Xq3pOLckrZEXLcF4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"A feeling of uneasy anticipation hangs over Washington ahead of the release of a redacted version of Robert Mueller 's report Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Many in the White House seem braced for bad news","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"-- which is odd","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"considering President Donald Trump has already claimed complete absolution from the special counsel .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"But that pessimism is also shared by the President 's Democratic enemies","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Once , Mueller 's report loomed as a moment of national catharsis","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that could finally lay out what happened in the bitter 2016 election","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"and put the Russian election meddling saga to rest .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"But after 2,800 subpoenas , 500 search warrants , 500 witness interviews","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"and partly because of a relentless campaign by Trump","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to discredit Mueller ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"it 's clear that such hopes were misplaced .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"The report will almost certainly leave everyone on both sides of the aisle unsatisfied","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and will only spark deeper divides in a nation","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that is already split down the middle over Trump .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"The drama","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"surrounding its conclusion","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"is now most likely to serve as a monument to Washington dysfunction , the irreconcilable viewpoints of warring political factions on common facts ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and to provide another data point for those","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"who believe","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"the current White House is determined to resist constraints on its power .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"One key reason why is the role of Attorney General William Barr ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who will release the Mueller report","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"-- shorn of grand jury testimony , classified material and evidence pertinent to active cases .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"His approach is all but certain to trigger a long legal battle","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"with Democrats","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"demanding a version of the report unfiltered by the administration .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"The attorney general 's statement last month","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that Mueller did not find collusion between the Trump campaign and Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"and the special counsel 's personal conclusion","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that there was not sufficient evidence of obstruction of justice ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"set a hugely helpful narrative for the President","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and inevitably politicized the unveiling of the report by Mueller","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"-- one of the rare people in Washington","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"who enjoys bipartisan respect .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Barr was already a controversial figure","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"--","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"after arguing in a memo to the Justice Department","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that Trump , as president , could not obstruct justice","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"before he was nominated .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"His comment last week","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that he believed","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"there was `` spying '' on the Trump campaign","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"-- a key White House talking point --","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"shattered any lingering chance","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that he would be seen as an honest arbiter ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"and furthered an impression","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that the administration was leaning on the scales of justice .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Democrats , Trump preemptively set bar for Mueller report","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Democrats , Trump preemptively set bar for Mueller report","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"05:41","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"One of the curiosities of the Mueller investigation is the way","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that Trump has often acted","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"as though he has something to hide ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"despite furiously protesting his innocence .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"If his tweets are any guide ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"he remains caught between nervous dread of what the report may conclude","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"and his vehement view","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that he 's the victim of a `` witch hunt .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"'' `` No Collusion - No Obstruction , ''","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Trump tweeted on Tuesday ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"not content to wait for the outcome of a report","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that Barr concluded","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"left him in no criminal jeopardy .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"His tweeting hit a new pitch of intensity on Wednesday morning .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"`` The Witch Hunt has been a total fraud on your President and the American people !","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"It was brought to you by Dirty Cops , Crooked Hillary and the DNC , ''","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"But the President is not alone in","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"experiencing an odd sense of limbo ahead of a moment","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that could help history define his presidency .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Current and former White House officials are fretting","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that the report could be politically damaging","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"and expose their own embarrassing testimony about the President ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"CNN reported .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"The White House spin in the days","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"leading up to the report 's release","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"has stressed Barr 's findings","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"delivered in a letter to Congress","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"in the hope","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"that Americans are ready to move on from Russia with the 2020 election ahead .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"`` We consider this to be case closed .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"That there was no collusion ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"there was no obstruction","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"which I do n't know","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"how you can interpret that any other way than total exoneration , ''","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Sanders said on Fox News Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"In their own way , Trump 's enemies in Washington are also reasoning","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"that the country may have deeper concerns than Russia ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"while still arguing","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that their constitutional duty requires them to call his behavior to account .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Democratic leaders ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"while stressing","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"that they see Barr as a partisan","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"who does not have the final word on the Russia saga ,","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"are still downplaying talk of impeachment ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"apparently hedging","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"in case the Mueller report is not as damaging to Trump","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"as many liberals had hoped .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi on Tuesday accused Barr of declaring","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"that Trump `` is above the law ''","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"but stressed in an interview with CNN","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"that she would wait","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"until seeing the report","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"before reacting .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Nonpartisan legal analysts are also concerned .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"They fear","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"vast redactions from the report will not only deprive Americans of evidence","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"they deserve","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"but will ignite ferocious legal battles .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"we should all get ready to feel quite disappointed in what we will see , ''","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"said CNN legal analyst Shan Wu on Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"`` The redactions are going to be so enormous","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"they are just going to swallow the entire report . ''","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":4},{"id":120,"text":"Trump legal team prepares","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"as DOJ says","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"Mueller report coming Thursday","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":4},{"id":124,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"Trump legal team prepares","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"as DOJ says","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Mueller report coming Thursday","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"03:04","depth":5},{"id":129,"text":"The drama","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"surrounding the report","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"is certain to tell a story","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"of how the President has suspended political gravity .","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"Barr reported to Congress","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"that Mueller did not find","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"that Trump 's team conspired with Russia in its election meddling effort","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"and that he had personally concluded","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"the evidence was not sufficient","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"to establish","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"that the President obstructed justice .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"But there is a clear possibility","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"that the report still contains evidence of questionable and unethical","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"-- just not criminal --","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"behavior by Trump 's team in the run up to the 2016 election .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"Russia watchers will be keen to see what Mueller made of the meeting in Trump Tower in the summer of 2016 , for instance , between members of Trump 's family and campaign team and Russians","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"promising `` dirt '' on Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"since Barr wrote","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"that Mueller did not make a final conclusion on obstruction","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"-- but sets out `` evidence on both sides of the question '' --","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"it is likely that Trump could come across in a very poor light ,","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"even appearing to have abused his power and the spirit , if not the letter of conventions ,","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"designed to ensure the independence of the Justice Department .","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"For any normal politician such a conclusion","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"-- though short of criminal jeopardy --","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"would likely spell disaster .","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"But Trump and his allies have mounted an effective propaganda campaign","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"to discredit Mueller 's findings ,","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"based on the premise","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"that the only issue is the hard-to-prove offense of `` collusion . ''","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"And so solid is Trump 's appeal to his political base","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"that it seems impossible any revelations by Mueller could cause GOP senators to split with the President in any Senate impeachment trial .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"Still , anything less than absolution by Mueller would also deprive Trump of the chance","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"to rid himself of the Russia cloud","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that could still cause complications in his 2020 reelection race","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"and is certain to help history define his presidency .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"That 's one reason why Trump 's lawyers are preparing their own rebuttal of the Mueller report .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"`` There ca n't be anything there","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"because there was no crime ,","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"there was no anything ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"the crime was committed by the other side .","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"This crime was all made up ,","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"it was all a fabrication , ''","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"he told KTSP television on Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"Though it 's clear that the Mueller report will not spell the end of the Russia intrigue","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"-- there are already calls for him to testify on Capitol Hill","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"--","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"the special counsel could still solve some overhanging mysteries .","depth":6},{"id":178,"text":"His report ,","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"presuming","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"the need","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"to keep intelligence sources and methods secret","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"does not preclude it ,","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"could contain the most detailed accounting yet of the Russian election operation .","depth":6},{"id":184,"text":"Mueller 's report could also help solve the mystery","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"of why he felt unable to render a conclusion","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"on whether Trump obstructed justice","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"in order to thwart the Russia investigation .","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"Trump 's opponents have argued","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"that his firing of then-FBI Director James Comey , assaults on the integrity of his then-Attorney General Jeff Sessions , attacks on the Mueller probe and apparent dangling of pardons amount to obstruction in plain sight .","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"It is not clear yet","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"whether Mueller agrees","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"-- and whether he opted","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"to leave such questions of presidential behavior to Congress .","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"Such questions ,","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"which lie at the center of the Russia investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"are likely to feed multiple probes","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"already underway in the Democratic House","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"that will continue to haunt Trump .","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"Republicans , meanwhile , are sure to portray the report as a reason","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"to launch new inquiries into the previous Obama administration and the genesis of FBI investigations of the Trump campaign .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":401,"left":319,"right":400,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":319,"left":249,"right":318,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":0,"right":248,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":248,"left":205,"right":247,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":1,"right":204,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":203,"left":2,"right":202,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":220,"right":246,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":214,"right":219,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":211,"right":213,"relation":"evalua